        <h1>pharmacist's Registeration</h1>
        <h3>you will receive acceptance/ rejection to you request in 2-3 days</h3>
    <div class="cont">
        <form method='post' action='/register/pharmacist'>
            Username: <br>
            <input type="text" id="user" name="username"> <br>
            Name: <br>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name"> <br>
